com.esri.mo2.map.core
Interface GroupElement

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Data, Element, Identifiable, MapData, Spatial
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseGroupElement
public interface GroupElement
extends Element

A GroupElement is an ordered collection of Element(s).

Each Element can be identified by either itself (a Element reference) or by the element index which is the element's index location within the the ordered collection.
